{"parentUuid":"0a160295-4d47-49ec-b5db-2037863504fe","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_20260222073150adcbdb6f18424fcb","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**华为 Mate 系列手机测试方法：**\n\n请尝试拨打以下代码：\n\n1. `*#*#2846579#*#*` (华为工程模式)\n2. `*#*#3646633#*#*` (通用工程模式)\n\n---\n\n**如果代码仍然无效，可以用手机自带测试：**\n\n进入：**设置 → 系统和更新 → 开发者选项**\n\n如果没有开发者选项：\n1. 设置 → 关于手机\n2. 连续点击\"版本号\" 7次启用\n\n启用后查看是否有 **硬件测试** 或 **音频测试** 选项。\n\n---\n\n**最简单的方法：**\n\n在手机上播放任意音乐或视频，看是否有声音。\n\n**如果您已通过 USB 连接手机到电脑**，我可以帮您：\n1. 安装 ADB 工具\n2. 通过电脑向手机发送音频测试命令\n\n请确认手机是否已连接到电脑。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":69,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":32000,"output_tokens":198,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"1f00e11a-f3d6-48e3-8d7a-e1f0220d013a","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:31:55.354Z"}
