{"parentUuid":"0c809100-0959-45b8-beed-6e206ee7726c","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_202602220731584334da5624d94178","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**华为 Mate X5 测试方法：**\n\n华为新款手机的工程模式代码经常被屏蔽。\n\n**请尝试以下方法：**\n\n---\n\n**方法一：手机自带测试**\n1. 进入 **设置**\n2. 搜索 **\"手机管家\"**\n3. 进入 **服务 → 服务中心 → 自行检测**\n4. 选择 **扬声器/听筒** 进行测试\n\n---\n\n**方法二：拨号界面测试**\n1. 打开拨号，输入 `*#*#6130#*#*`\n2. 或输入 `*#*#2846579159#*#*`\n\n---\n\n**方法三：会员中心**\n1. 打开 **会员中心** App\n2. **服务 → 一键检测**\n3. 选择 **扬声器** 测试\n\n---\n\n**如果以上都不行：**\n\n请播放一段音乐或视频测试是否有声音。\n\n**如果手机已通过 USB 连接到电脑**，我可以帮您用 ADB 命令测试。\n\n请告诉我：\n1. 手机是否已连接电脑？\n2. 扬声器是完全没声音，还是声音异常？"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":16,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":32256,"output_tokens":231,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"c037b00b-c8ef-4c26-b5f4-8f31c1d2773b","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:32:02.948Z"}
