{"parentUuid":"8525ad80-b65e-45ee-bc41-46135b1d2d58","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_20260222073203181890505e7f46d4","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"扬声器完全没声音。\n\n**请按顺序排查：**\n\n---\n\n**1. 最简单 - 检查音量和静音**\n- 按音量+键，确保不是静音\n- 下拉控制中心，检查是否勾选了静音\n- 检查是否有耳机或蓝牙设备连接（拔掉试试）\n\n---\n\n**2. 重启手机**\n- 长按电源键 → 重启\n\n---\n\n**3. 用手机自带测试**\n- **会员中心 → 服务 → 一键检测 → 扬声器**\n- 或 **拨号 → 键盘 → 输入 *#*#6130#*#***\n\n---\n\n**4. 备份数据后恢复出厂**（慎用）\n- 设置 → 系统和更新 → 重置 → 恢复出厂设置\n\n---\n\n**如果以上都不行：**\n\n这是硬件故障的可能性较大。Mate X5 是折叠屏，排线容易受损。\n\n**建议：**\n- 联系华为客服 950800\n- 或前往附近华为授权服务中心检修\n\n---\n\n**如果手机已连接到电脑**，我可以尝试用 ADB 命令进一步诊断软件问题。请问手机是否已通过 USB 连接？"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":123,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":32384,"output_tokens":260,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"2329043a-2b7d-44e0-b9a8-ea8cc7aee8c6","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:32:09.741Z"}
