{"parentUuid":"db4ac4e5-ff60-4985-b76d-4c16536899c7","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_20260222073352fe5fcee844b541ff","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"检测到 **HDB Interface**，说明手机是华为特有的调试模式。\n\n---\n\n**需要安装华为手机助手 (HiSuite)：**\n\n1. 下载地址：https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/hisuite/\n2. 安装后会自动安装 HDB 驱动\n3. 安装完成后，在手机上允许 HDB 调试\n\n---\n\n**或者更简单的方法：**\n\n既然手机已连接，请在手机上直接测试扬声器：\n\n1. **拨打 *#*#6130#*#*** (硬件测试)\n2. **播放一段音乐**\n3. **会员中心 → 服务 → 一键检测**\n\n---\n\n**ADB 对华为手机支持有限**，因为华为用的是自家的 HDB 协议。\n\n**您手机扬声器是完全没声音吗？** 如果是，大概率是硬件问题（折叠屏排线故障），建议送修。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":93,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":34176,"output_tokens":186,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"d651451b-4e17-452c-82ae-dd6ead59026c","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:33:55.381Z"}
