{"parentUuid":"c33917f2-eae7-482e-881f-7264cc61cc3e","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_20260222073430db6bd5f3015e4c35","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mate X5 是新款手机，华为已屏蔽了大部分工程模式代码。\n\n---\n\n**请尝试手机自带诊断：**\n\n1. **会员中心 App → 服务 → 服务体验 → 一键检测 → 扬声器**\n\n2. **拨号 → 键盘 → 输入 *#*#2846579159#*#***\n\n---\n\n**如果都不行，这是最直接的测试方法：**\n\n打开 **YouTube** 或 **音乐播放器**，播放任意视频/音乐，看看有没有声音。\n\n---\n\n**请告诉我：**\n1. 手机是完全没声音（音乐、视频、铃声都没有）？\n2. 还是只是某些情况没声音？\n\n如果是**完全没声音**，Mate X5 折叠屏的扬声器排线故障概率较高，建议：\n\n- 拨打华为客服 **950800**\n- 或前往 **华为授权服务中心** 检测"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":38,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":34432,"output_tokens":186,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"4a73203b-3761-400c-92d1-242c1b832811","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:34:34.745Z"}
