{"parentUuid":"861a2142-4c7d-48c8-87c0-560e211298e8","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_20260222073555a6f80cf61eb24bbe","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**手机完全没声音，这是硬件故障的可能性很高。**\n\nMate X5 是折叠屏，铰链处的扬声器排线容易因频繁折叠而受损。\n\n---\n\n**在送修前，请最后确认：**\n\n1. **音量键是否有效？** 按音量+看屏幕是否有音量条显示\n\n2. **是否有蓝牙设备连接？**\n   - 设置 → 蓝牙，关闭蓝牙试试\n\n3. **重启手机**（长按电源键 → 重启）\n\n4. **备份数据后恢复出厂设置**\n   - 设置 → 系统和更新 → 重置 → 恢复出厂设置\n\n---\n\n**如果以上都不行，是硬件故障。**\n\n**建议送修：**\n\n- 华为客服：**950800**\n- 或在 **会员中心 App** 预约附近的服务中心\n\nMate X5 扬声器故障在折叠屏中比较常见，通常需要更换排线或扬声器模块。\n\n---\n\n**如果您已连接电脑，我还可以尝试用 ADB 命令做最后的软件层面诊断。** 需要我试试吗？"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":110,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":34560,"output_tokens":238,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"1ae611e6-5fed-4c5c-85a4-515e8cc3b825","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:35:59.185Z"}
