{"parentUuid":"aa1242a3-bfb0-40f0-81bc-405e6d296b2b","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_20260222073757aa5ceb7858a44c69","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个理解可能有误。**MIDI 模式不会禁用手机扬声器**，它只是改变了 USB 传输协议。\n\n---\n\n**请先确认问题：**\n\n1. **手机扬声器在没连接电脑之前就是没声音的吗？**\n2. **还是连接电脑后才没声音的？**\n\n---\n\n**如果是连接后才没声音，请尝试：**\n\n1. **断开 USB 连接**，测试扬声器是否恢复\n2. **更改 USB 模式为 \"文件传输\"**\n3. **在手机设置中关闭 \"USB 音频输出\"**（如果有此选项）\n\n---\n\n**如果手机一直没声音（无论是否连接电脑）**，那就是**硬件故障**，与 USB 模式无关。\n\n---\n\n请告诉我：扬声器是**一直没声音**，还是**连接电脑后才没声音**？"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":54,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":41472,"output_tokens":173,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"f3101ef6-83ad-43d3-afdb-18e509abba5a","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:38:01.763Z"}
