{"parentUuid":"5cbeae9c-5b75-4240-ae14-a9f43b0d9bbe","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_202602220739463d9fb3389fbd4b19","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"那就是**硬件故障**，与 USB 连接无关。\n\n---\n\n**结论：扬声器硬件损坏**\n\nMate X5 折叠屏的扬声器排线容易因频繁折叠而受损，这是常见故障。\n\n---\n\n**建议送修：**\n\n1. **华为客服**：950800\n2. **会员中心 App** → 预约服务中心\n3. **华为授权服务中心**：检修/更换扬声器模块\n\n---\n\n**送修前建议：**\n\n1. **备份数据**（可能需要重置或更换主板）\n2. **带好购机凭证**（如果在保修期内）\n\n---\n\n如果需要，我可以帮您**查找最近的华为授权服务中心**。请告诉我您的城市。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":104,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":41600,"output_tokens":148,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"ec7f9981-9fef-4988-9bef-8623b9d5f0cf","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:39:51.022Z"}
