{"parentUuid":"302d7b9c-e66c-4e7a-b1a2-d17206a7530b","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_202602220743588d542c56f64e44f0","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"华为 HDB 无法用标准 ADB 连接。我需要您在手机上配合操作：\n\n---\n\n**全自动修复需要在手机上操作（因为华为限制）：**\n\n---\n\n**【第一步】关闭开发者选项中可能禁用扬声器的设置**\n\n进入：**设置 → 系统和更新 → 开发者选项**\n\n找到并**关闭**以下选项：\n- USB 音频\n- 禁用绝对音量\n- 模拟辅助设备\n- 任何包含 \"audio\" 或 \"调试\" 的选项\n\n---\n\n**【第二步】完全关闭开发者选项**\n\n在开发者选项页面，把顶部的**开关关掉**\n\n---\n\n**【第三步】重启手机**\n\n长按电源键 → 重启\n\n---\n\n**【第四步】测试**\n\n播放音乐或视频，检查是否有声音\n\n---\n\n请按以上步骤操作并告诉我结果。如果仍无效，我们继续尝试其他方法。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":40,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":46848,"output_tokens":187,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"fc8cee61-12dd-4e9b-bb3d-e65d79fc9e74","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:44:03.571Z"}
