{"parentUuid":"2a5c8e84-e5ac-4a72-b08f-36a4e4ab2c1e","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"1be01e35-b1a6-473e-972f-6126cd4ad7de","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"agile-tickling-newell","message":{"id":"msg_202602220746140410b7ae243c4ca5","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"继续尝试下一个方案。\n\n---\n\n**请在手机上操作：**\n\n---\n\n**【方案一】清除音量设置缓存**\n\n1. **设置 → 应用**\n2. **点击右上角\"三个点\" → 显示系统进程**\n3. **搜索 \"设置\" 或 \"声音\"**\n4. **进入 → 存储 → 清除缓存**\n5. **重启手机**\n\n---\n\n**【方案二】重置声音设置**\n\n1. **设置 → 声音和振动**\n2. **进入每个子菜单（铃声、媒体音量、通知音量）**\n3. **确保音量调到最大，且没有静音**\n4. **检查以下选项是否开启，如有则关闭：**\n   - 勿扰模式\n   - 定向音 / 空间音频\n   - 耳机效果 / 辅助听力\n\n---\n\n**【方案三】尝试拨号代码**\n\n在拨号界面输入：\n- `*#*#2846579159#*#*`\n- 或 `*#*#3646633#*#*`\n\n如果能进入工程菜单，找到 **Audio** 或 **扬声器** 选项进行测试或重置。\n\n---\n\n请尝试以上方案并告诉我结果。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":103,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":46976,"output_tokens":263,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"c9ee3fde-8597-4457-8374-a6e7e1f75440","timestamp":"2026-02-21T23:46:20.508Z"}
